  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Advanced damage model of ships. All ships are close to their historical prototypes.<br></li><li>High influence of visibility and weather conditions.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1738890/extras/24a6e48049dae0b577770049f5e26e80.poster.avif?t=1749767646\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1738890/extras/24a6e48049dae0b577770049f5e26e80.webm?t=1749767646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1738890/extras/24a6e48049dae0b577770049f5e26e80.mp4?t=1749767646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Damage control system. Player can manually manage crew to repair modules, patch holes, fight fire, and so on to prevent ship from exiting battle and sinking.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1738890/extras/6045ffe608f725fac2306e069f5818a3.poster.avif?t=1749767646\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1738890/extras/6045ffe608f725fac2306e069f5818a3.webm?t=1749767646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1738890/extras/6045ffe608f725fac2306e069f5818a3.mp4?t=1749767646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Fleet commander career single player global map campaign.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Advanced damage model of ships. All ships are close to their historical prototypes.<br></li><li>High influence of visibility and weather conditions.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1738890/extras/24a6e48049dae0b577770049f5e26e80.poster.avif?t=1749767646\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1738890/extras/24a6e48049dae0b577770049f5e26e80.webm?t=1749767646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1738890/extras/24a6e48049dae0b577770049f5e26e80.mp4?t=1749767646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Damage control system. Player can manually manage crew to repair modules, patch holes, fight fire, and so on to prevent ship from exiting battle and sinking.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1738890/extras/6045ffe608f725fac2306e069f5818a3.poster.avif?t=1749767646\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1738890/extras/6045ffe608f725fac2306e069f5818a3.webm?t=1749767646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1738890/extras/6045ffe608f725fac2306e069f5818a3.mp4?t=1749767646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Fleet commander career single player global map campaign.</li></ul>",
